 {\n            assertEquals(\"Could not initialize class groovy.lang.GroovySystem\", error.getMessage());\n        }\n    }\n", "newText": "    void resolvesCompilerGeneratedClassResolverForReachableJdkType() throws Throwable {\n        Class<?> resolvedClass = (Class<?>) classResolver().invokeWithArguments(\"java.lang.String\");\n\n        assertSame(String.class, resolvedClass);\n    }\n"}, {"oldText": "\n    @Test\n    void parsesHtmlResponsesWithTagSoupParser() {\n        Response response = new ResponseBuilder()\n                .setStatusCode(200)\n                .setContentType(\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\")\n                .setBody(\"\"\"\n                        <html>\n                          <body>\n                            <h1>Rest Assured</h1>\n                            <p>HTML content parser</p>\n                          </body>\n                        </html>\n                        \"\"\")\n                .build();\n        ResponseParserRegistrar parserRegistrar = new ResponseParserRegistrar();\n        ContentParser contentParser = new ContentParser();\n\n        Object parsed = contentParser.parse(response, parserRegistrar, RestAssuredConfig.config(), true);\n\n        GPathResult html = assertInstanceOf(GPathResult.class, parsed);\n        assertThat(html.text()).contains(\"Rest Assured\", \"HTML content parser\");\n    }\n", "newText": ""}]}
